NOTICE: This software is designed to support individuals struggling with
gambling addiction. It is provided as a support tool and does not replace
professional medical or psychological treatment. If you or someone you know
is struggling with gambling addiction, please seek help from qualified
healthcare professionals.

Emergency Resources (Brazil):
- CVV (Centro de Valorização da Vida): 188 (24/7)
- Jogadores Anônimos: www.jogadoresanonimos.com.br

